Windows 11 Outline
Windows 11 Outline is a bright flat icon pack. These color graphics will fit any desktop or web application, and mobile app screens. As well as Cute Color, Hand Drawn Color, and Color icon packs, Windows 11 Outline icons effectively work as clipart images for infographics, custom cards, or presentations.
Download the color icons on various themes for user interfaces and graphic design. Or edit the images you need right here. The free graphics are pixel perfect and available in both png and vector.
As well, welcome to check new icons and popular icons in 30+ design styles.
